Brazil Offers Ukraine Joint Black Sea Shelf Oil, Gas Exploration

-- B y   K a t e r y n a   C h o u r s i n a
-- 
2011-08-23T15:59:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-23/brazil-offers-ukraine-joint-black-sea-shelf-oil-gas-exploration.html
Brazil  wants Ukraine to jointly
explore for natural gas and crude on the Black Sea shelf, said
Antonio Fernando Cruz de Mello, Brazil’s ambassador to Ukraine.  Experts from Petroleo Brasileiro SA, the Rio de Janeiro-
based oil producer known as Petrobras, are interested in
cooperating with Ukrainian companies to jointly search for
hydrocarbons in the sea, the ambassador said today at a meeting
with Ukraine’s Prime Minister  Mykola Azarov , according to a
statement on the government website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kateryna Choursina  in Kiev at 
 kchoursina@bloomberg.net ;  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Claudia Carpenter at 
 ccarpenter2@bloomberg.net  